	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas bona fide accepi per cursorem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l907" cert="high">Campidonensem</placeName>, optime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>; verum quum non aliud continerent quam necessariam quidem, sed veterem querimoniam neque aliunde mihi quicquam advenisset, non arbitrabar e re futurum, ut meis te obruerem, nisi aliqua amplior mihi ad te scribendi occasio fuisset oblata.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Curabo autem, ut <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> tuas confestim accipiat et ut alterae ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8426" cert="high">Paulum Rasdorferum</persName> itidem perferantur, qui hodie in agro Abtzellano apud ecclesiam <placeName type="citizen_name">Trogensem</placeName> concionatur.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Coniicio <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculum</persName> brevi ad vos cessurum cum familia sua, vellem eum tibi quam commendatissimum esse ob eximiam suam eruditionem et sanctitatem et quod unice te et amat et praedicat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Augustani <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8354">Georgium Laetum</persName> dimisere sat honorifice, ut audio, sed nulla alia caussa summotum, quam quod sanam doctrinam mira libertate hactenus defendit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quo sit abiturus, nescio; sed dominus ei de nidulo providebit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Unser armer <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1055">Ferechtus</persName> ligt zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name">Kirch an der Egg</placeName> imm <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572">Wirtenberger</placeName> land.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ain eerlicher, frommer kouffman, der von dess kaysers sachen vil wüssens und erfarens, hat mir in gehaim anzayt, das die kayß[erliche] m[ajesta]t diss herbstz khainen burlichen krieg fuͤren werde; aber uff das künftig jar sölle ain söllich gwaltig rüstung angesechen und fürgenomen sein, dergleychen man noch disser jaren nit gesechen habe; niemand mög aber wüssen, wider wen und worzuͦgegen.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Endtlich aber ist für und für offentlich anzaygen, er werde die freyhait der <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862">Schweytzer</placeName> onangefochten nit laßen, vertrauwe auch, teutsche nation in ghorsamen nit zuͦ behalten, er mach dann die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862">Schweytzer</placeName> vor allen dingen ouch gehorsam etc.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale et brevi longiores expectato.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l473" cert="high">Sangalli</placeName> nono die Septembris anno MDXLVIIIo.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ex animo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8049" cert="high">Ioachimus Vadianus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Doctissimo et pientissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinorum</placeName> episcopo, domino suo colendissimo.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
